    <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/afghanistan-ministry-of-counter-narcotics-national-drug-control-strategy"/>
    <title>Afghanistan Ministry of Counter-Narcotics' National Drug Control Strategy </title>
    <category>Publication</category>
    <summary/>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;The UK supports the Afghan Government in implementing its National Drug Control Strategy. It is a comprehensive approach which covers a range of activities to counter the drugs trade. These include building government institutions and law enforcement capacity, targeted eradication programmes and the development of alternative livelihoods, information and education campaigns and engagement with countries in the region. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Read the attached updated five-year strategy for tackling the illicit drug problem in Afghanistan.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
