    <title>The New Armed Forces Pension Scheme - Initial Consultation</title>
    <category>Consultation</category>
    <summary>The initial stage of the Future Armed Forces Pension Consultation is now closed.</summary>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Outline Scheme Design document has launched the &lt;a rel="external" href="http://www.mod.uk/DefenceInternet/AboutDefence/CorporatePublications/ConsultationsandCommunications/PublicConsultations/TheNewArmedForcesPensionSchemeFinalConsultation.htm"&gt;final consultation phase&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Details of the initial consultation can be found in the Initial Consultation document in the hyperlink below and in the associated Presentation and Script, which can be found under Related pages on the right-hand side.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The results of the initial consultation stage can be read in the ‘Initial Consultation Results’ document under Related pages on the right-hand side.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;MOD would like to thank all those who participated in the initial consultation.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
